SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Thursday March 19t
 h) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with
  **Love Songs that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well 
 over 36 years.\nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, in
 cluding some of our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time a
 fter 8:30 pm (Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in t
 he evening as well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your fir
 st time attending :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Fle
 mming\n(Songwriter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Lo
 ve Songs that Stir the Soul (Friday\, March 27th)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*O
 riginal Lyrics and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*S
 tory songs\, love songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our cultu
 re\, our past\, our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be playin
 g a mix of songs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditiona
 l Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy List
 ening\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie R
 ock/Po**p and many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready to 
 have an amazing auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\n\
 n\\*You can come on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:30
  pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer so
 ngwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my own
  songs since 1990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, r
 omance\, memories\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universal\
 , heartfelt and often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can 
 kindly send through e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.com
 **\n\n-Anything you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help support 
 this meaningful musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom li
 nk:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events:
 **\nYour songs are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and momen
 ts we've all felt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwrite
 r whose lyrics stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life int
 o beautiful poetry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.L
 .\nSteve\, thank you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspiri
 ng music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, they 
 calm me and energize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next in
 vite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a l
 ong day. Keep up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank y
 ou so much for a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve! 
 I am excited to hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely son
 gs and a great vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a b
 etter way to close my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly en
 joyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nTha
 nks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joined.
 \n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
